 the deal with the million side effects they list at the end?&nbsp;</p><p s=
tyle=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em=
 0;">I&#8217;m here to talk to you about the world of pharma marketing and =
